"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-entertainment-gaming-1981643-ps-plus-december-2024-games-line-up-It-Takes-Two\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Sonyhas officially unveiled thenew PlayStation Plus games for December 2024, and it's a pretty decent selection to end the year.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Available from the morning of December 3, the latest batch of freePS4andPS5games are headlined by the sublime It Takes Two.\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The co-operative adventure game is the perfect choice forPlayStation Plus, especially if you have a friend willing to play along with you.\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The winner of multiple game of the year awards, It Takes Two is directed by Josef Fares, whose previous credits include Brothers: A Tale of Two Sons, and A Way Out.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 473, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josef_Fares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Josef Fares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josef_Fares\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josef_Fares\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With an Overwhelmingly Positive rating on Steam, the game sees players team up to solve puzzles after being transformed into dolls by a magic spell.\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only is the game packed with delightful puzzles and fiendish brainteasers, but it also boasts a powerful narrative that's both funny and full of heart.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It Takes Two will be joined by Aliens Dark Descent, which is a critically-acclaimed strategy game set in the Alien universe.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extraterrestrial_life\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.959206717656757e-30, \"text\": \"Aliens\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extraterrestrial_life\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extraterrestrial_life\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Aliens: Dark Descent, command a squad of hardened Colonial Marines to stop a terrifying Xenomorph outbreak on Planet Lethe,\\\" reads the official description.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corps_of_Colonial_Marines\", \"score\": 0.9999999994636255, \"rank\": 5.364087534614072e-10, \"text\": \"Colonial Marines\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corps_of_Colonial_Marines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corps_of_Colonial_Marines\"}, {\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(creature_in_Alien_franchise)\", \"score\": 0.9989083170888351, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xenomorph\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(creature_in_Alien_franchise)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(creature_in_Alien_franchise)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lead your soldiers in real-time combat against iconic Xenomorphs, rogue operatives from the insatiable Weyland-Yutani Corporation, and a host of horrifying creatures new to the Alien franchise.\\\"\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1213, \"end\": 1223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(creature_in_Alien_franchise)\", \"score\": 0.9990025659554683, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xenomorphs\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(creature_in_Alien_franchise)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(creature_in_Alien_franchise)\"}, {\"begin\": 1262, \"end\": 1276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(franchise)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999797637, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Weyland-Yutani\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(franchise)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(franchise)\"}, {\"begin\": 1336, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(franchise)\", \"score\": 0.9999999618546561, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alien franchise\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(franchise)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(franchise)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like many of the best strategy games, Aliens Dark Descent utilises a permadeath feature, which means that when your squad members die, they are gone for good.\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extraterrestrial_life\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.959206717656757e-30, \"text\": \"Aliens\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extraterrestrial_life\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extraterrestrial_life\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I always feel like this ups the stakes and increases the tension, especially when you lose a powerful member of your squad that has been there since the beginning.\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Elsewhere, PS Plus Essential subscribers will also be able to download TemTem from December 3.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1691, \"end\": 1698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PlayStation_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"PS Plus\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PlayStation_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PlayStation_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 1751, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Temtem\", \"score\": 0.669467902590356, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TemTem\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Temtem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Temtem\"}]}, 